# Runtime-generated build artifacts and conversation state.
# .graphbus/ is created by 'graphbus build' and populated by each session;
# its contents (agents.json, graph.json, topics.json, build_summary.json,
# conversation_history.json) are fully regenerated on every run and contain
# local machine paths and potentially user conversation data.  They have no
# place in version control.
